  "title": "Finance Associate",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li><strong>Financial Reporting & Analysis:</strong> Prepare financial statements, analyze data, identify trends, and create reports for management.</li><li><strong>Budgeting & Forecasting:</strong> Assist in creating budgets, forecasting financial performance, and tracking performance against goals.</li><li><strong>Operations & Transactions:</strong> Manage invoices, process payments (AP/AR), reconcile bank statements, and handle expense reports.</li><li><strong>Compliance & Auditing:</strong> Ensure adherence to regulations, assist with tax filings (GST, income tax), and support external audits.</li><li><strong>System Support:</strong> Help with implementing new accounting software and maintaining financial records.</li><li><strong>Internal Support:</strong> Provide financial guidance and support to other departments, advising on fiscal procedures. </li></ul><p>Key Skills & Qualifications:</p><ul><li>Bachelor's degree in Accounting, Finance, or related field.</li><li>Strong analytical and data management skills.</li><li>Excellent attention to detail and accuracy.</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills for collaborating with teams and management.</li><li>Knowledge of financial regulations and accounting principles.</li><li>Experience with accounting software (e.g., <a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=Dynamics+365&sca_esv=5e774f803d6df108&rlz=1C1ONGR_enSG1132SG1132&sxsrf=ANbL-n5wEPR5qZlkNj8O9GX87GNYurRzeA%3A1769345402707&ei=ehF2acjwKtCsseMP1diesQM&oq=finance+assoc+jd&gs_-yBwM5LjK4B-4FwgcGMC4xMS4xyAcZgAgA&sclient=gws-wiz-serp&ved=2ahUKEwjLhN-_3aaSAxX8yzgGHc8MKEYQgK4QegYIAAgGEAY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Dynamics 365</a>) and system implementation is a plus. </li></ul>",
